\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The passage says we worship the God of Hope\
\ls7\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But that is not who I think most worship...\
