\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 There are two extremes I think many people have when they think of God\
\ls7\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 It starts with The God of Now and then goes to the God of Never\
\ls7\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The God of Now\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl352\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I want it now...I\'92ll pray for it now...a pastor told me if I pray for something that i can do all things through Christ.\
